  <brief_title>Study Evaluating Subcutaneous Methylnaltrexone For Treatment Of Opioid-Induced Constipation In Patients With Advanced Illness</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled Study Of A Fixed Dose Of Subcutaneous Methylnaltrexone In Adults With Advanced Illness And Opioid-Induced Constipation: Efficacy, Safety, And Additional Health Outcomes</official_title>
  <sponsors>
